  "key": "D major",
  "genre": [
    "Ballad",
    "Ambient"
  ],
  "difficultyLevel": 3,
  "lyrics": "I know the child in you that speaks all through your blood I feel inscribed by your fear If you just listen here Maybe you can hear Different thoughts beyond the ones you Tell yourself to fear Tell yourself it's real You tell you all That you'll never know Through experiences you breathe a little Through experience you find The message in the bottle of your own mind And then you heal Pass the doors in the back of your mind And find the real inside of the fear Yeah, colors come, colors go And so does the soil from which you grew And the power of the sun you try to steal I know you from the beginning of the track I hope you know you're okay And there's no going back Always know there's no going back From your life, from that big bang became you Don't lose that view of you Time passes and time does It's just the story of us all Love no tears Love finds the dark and makes it free To be you and me There's gotta be a dark side There's gotta be a light side Feeling happiness inside of you There's no reason to hide or worry or judge yourself From everything you told yourself you'd be Let it gently waste off your arms down Until your fingertips and let it all go Let it all go From your child to your toes",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 18.059999465942383,
      "text": "I know the child in you that speaks all through your blood",
      "start": 1.5199999809265137
    },
    {
      "end": 25.31999969482422,
      "text": "I feel inscribed by your fear",
      "start": 18.059999465942383
    },
    {
      "end": 30.360000610351562,
      "text": "If you just listen here",
      "start": 26.059999465942383
    },
    {
      "end": 35.70000076293945,
      "text": "Maybe you can hear",
      "start": 31.059999465942383
    },
    {
      "end": 41.380001068115234,
      "text": "Different thoughts beyond the ones you",
      "start": 35.7400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 44.400001525878906,
      "text": "Tell yourself to fear",
      "start": 42.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 48,
      "text": "Tell yourself it's real",
      "start": 45.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 52.599998474121094,
      "text": "You tell you all",
      "start": 48.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 56.41999816894531,
      "text": "That you'll never know",
      "start": 53.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 59.97999954223633,
      "text": "Through experiences you breathe a little",
      "start": 56.41999816894531
    },
    {
      "end": 63.060001373291016,
      "text": "Through experience you find",
      "start": 59.97999954223633
    },
    {
      "end": 68.80000305175781,
      "text": "The message in the bottle of your own mind",
      "start": 63.060001373291016
    },
    {
      "end": 72.31999969482422,
      "text": "And then you heal",
      "start": 69.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 78.18000030517578,
      "text": "Pass the doors in the back of your mind",
      "start": 73.58000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 84.13999938964844,
      "text": "And find the real inside of the fear",
      "start": 78.18000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 88.62000274658203,
      "text": "Yeah, colors come, colors go",
      "start": 84.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 94.62000274658203,
      "text": "And so does the soil from which you grew",
      "start": 88.62000274658203
    },
    {
      "end": 98.76000213623047,
      "text": "And the power of the sun you try to steal",
      "start": 94.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 106.69999694824219,
      "text": "I know you from the beginning of the track",
      "start": 98.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 110.87999725341797,
      "text": "I hope you know you're okay",
      "start": 106.69999694824219
    },
    {
      "end": 116.4000015258789,
      "text": "And there's no going back",
      "start": 111.76000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 124.33999633789062,
      "text": "Always know there's no going back",
      "start": 118.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 132.9600067138672,
      "text": "From your life, from that big bang became you",
      "start": 124.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 141.5800018310547,
      "text": "Don't lose that view of you",
      "start": 133.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 147.82000732421875,
      "text": "Time passes and time does",
      "start": 142.5
    },
    {
      "end": 154.3800048828125,
      "text": "It's just the story of us all",
      "start": 148.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 159.13999938964844,
      "text": "Love no tears",
      "start": 155.9600067138672
    },
    {
      "end": 163.67999267578125,
      "text": "Love finds the dark and makes it free",
      "start": 159.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 169.16000366210938,
      "text": "To be you and me",
      "start": 164.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 171.75999450683594,
      "text": "There's gotta be a dark side",
      "start": 169.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 173.66000366210938,
      "text": "There's gotta be a light side",
      "start": 171.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 175.6999969482422,
      "text": "Feeling happiness inside of you",
      "start": 173.66000366210938
    },
    {
      "end": 180.13999938964844,
      "text": "There's no reason to hide or worry or judge yourself",
      "start": 175.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 184.74000549316406,
      "text": "From everything you told yourself you'd be",
      "start": 180.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 189.94000244140625,
      "text": "Let it gently waste off your arms down",
      "start": 185.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 196.94000244140625,
      "text": "Until your fingertips and let it all go",
      "start": 189.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 200.77999877929688,
      "text": "Let it all go",
      "start": 198.6999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 204.24000549316406,
      "text": "From your child to your toes",
      "start": 200.77999877929688
    }
  ],
